item.title: Final Group Project: AirBnB analytics
item.description: Introduction In our final group assignment we are going to analyse data about Airbnb listings and fit a model to predict the total cost for two people staying 4 nights in an AirBnB in a city. item.title: About
item.description: Ray Park was born in Seoul, South Korea, and grew up in Boston, United States of America. He studied Mathematics at King’s College London and worked at PwC UK as an audit associate. He is studying Financial Analysis at London Business School.
